                            <h6 class="fw-black text-dark text-uppercase tracking-tight mb-1">Spaced Repetition System (SRS)</h6>
                            <p class="text-muted small fw-bold mb-0">NipponQuest utilizes an algorithmic SRS. Cards you struggle with will appear more frequently, while cards you know well will be pushed further into the future to optimize your memory retention.</p>
