                            <h6 class="fw-black text-dark text-uppercase tracking-tight mb-1">Creating & Editing Decks</h6>
                            <p class="text-muted small fw-bold mb-0">Click <strong>Create New</strong> to forge an empty deck. You can add Japanese text, meanings, and attach image/audio files manually.</p>
